WEBVTT

1
00:00:32.450 --> 00:00:33.659
Previously on Raising Kanan...

2
00:00:33.826 --> 00:00:35.536
In Chinese mythology.

3
00:00:35.703 --> 00:00:37.580
there's a monster called Hundun.

4
00:00:37.747 --> 00:00:40.332
A blind. deaf. faceless demon.

5
00:00:40.499 --> 00:00:42.376
Hundun is chaos.

6
00:00:46.505 --> 00:00:47.298
Evil.

7
00:00:47.465 --> 00:00:49.091
Corrupting and polluting

8
00:00:49.258 --> 00:00:50.760
all that it touches.

9
00:00:50.926 --> 00:00:53.471
Raq hired some dirty police
to kill your friend.

10
00:00:53.637 --> 00:00:56.599
What's most scary
about Hundun's true evil...

11
00:00:56.766 --> 00:00:58.768
- We in business. Hafiz.
- Isn't what it does...

12
00:00:58.934 --> 00:01:00.811
You gon' do what they won't?

13
00:01:00.936 --> 00:01:01.936
Where is it?

14
00:01:02.688 --> 00:01:04.482
But that it can't see itself.

15
00:01:04.607 --> 00:01:07.985
Just 'cause you didn't see me

16
00:01:08.152 --> 00:01:09.820
didn't mean I didn't see you.

17
00:01:09.987 --> 00:01:12.531
It doesn't know that it's a monster.

18
00:01:14.784 --> 00:01:17.119
Just like you.

19
00:01:17.286 --> 00:01:18.579
We both got family. 'Nique.

20
00:01:18.704 --> 00:01:20.664
I'm a street nigga
who do street nigga shit.

21
00:01:20.831 --> 00:01:23.375
I'm ready to go back to war next to y'all.

22
00:01:23.542 --> 00:01:25.586
If you want work. I got work for you.

23
00:01:25.753 --> 00:01:27.146
Both of you get in the fuckin' car.

24
00:01:27.170 --> 00:01:28.398
Come on. baby. It's gon' be all right.

25
00:01:28.422 --> 00:01:29.256
Let's go. nigga.

26
00:01:29.423 --> 00:01:30.966
But you need to step up

27
00:01:31.091 --> 00:01:32.384
and take care of your daughter.

28
00:01:32.551 --> 00:01:34.136
I know... You don't think I know that?

29
00:01:34.303 --> 00:01:35.447
And I am worried you're gonna do

30
00:01:35.471 --> 00:01:36.847
somethin' crazy about Famous.

31
00:01:36.972 --> 00:01:38.015
Famous was my brother.

32
00:01:38.182 --> 00:01:39.182
But he wouldn't want you

33
00:01:39.265 --> 00:01:40.643
to fuck yourself up for him.

34
00:01:40.810 --> 00:01:42.311
There's no world

35
00:01:42.478 --> 00:01:44.188
where the murder of a cop
goes unanswered.

36
00:01:44.354 --> 00:01:46.315
Squeeze hard on anyone you can.

37
00:01:46.482 --> 00:01:47.691
I'm police.

38
00:01:47.817 --> 00:01:48.901
She's safe with me.

39
00:01:49.026 --> 00:01:50.360
They found the Jane Doe

40
00:01:50.527 --> 00:01:51.946
in a stairwell over at Edgemere.

41
00:01:52.071 --> 00:01:53.632
One of the tenants had said
that they saw

42
00:01:53.656 --> 00:01:55.056
a Black woman leaving the apartment

43
00:01:55.115 --> 00:01:56.509
where we think your friend
was murdered.

44
00:01:56.533 --> 00:01:58.202
Call the police.

45
00:01:58.327 --> 00:02:00.222
tell 'em some white boy
with tattoos came in here

46
00:02:00.246 --> 00:02:01.686
and did all of that to these people.

47
00:02:04.959 --> 00:02:08.294
Phil Russo and his fuckin' gang
of misfits in Jersey

48
00:02:08.461 --> 00:02:10.172
think they can go toe-to-toe with me now.

49
00:02:10.297 --> 00:02:12.466
I overstepped. and I apologize.

50
00:02:15.261 --> 00:02:17.429
We look out for ours on this side.

51
00:02:17.596 --> 00:02:19.682
You got the streets wired
with these bike niggas.

52
00:02:19.849 --> 00:02:21.350
You and me join forces?

53
00:02:21.475 --> 00:02:22.619
We want a bigger piece of the pie

54
00:02:22.643 --> 00:02:23.853
out on Southside. Jamaica.

55
00:02:24.019 --> 00:02:25.396
And we got our own supplier.

56
00:02:25.563 --> 00:02:27.147
We bring together you and Unique

57
00:02:27.314 --> 00:02:28.750
and then connect you with our nephew.

58
00:02:28.774 --> 00:02:30.192
Niggas call me Breeze.

59
00:02:30.359 --> 00:02:31.359
Word.

60
00:02:32.111 --> 00:02:34.196
You don't know that it was Raq. Kanan.

61
00:02:34.363 --> 00:02:35.990
If you ain't with me. you against me.

62
00:02:37.950 --> 00:02:39.034
Why'd you kill Krystal?

63
00:02:39.201 --> 00:02:40.828
I didn't kill your girlfriend.

64
00:02:40.953 --> 00:02:42.371
I know you killed Fame too.

65
00:02:42.538 --> 00:02:45.040
I'm done making excuses for you
and for me.

66
00:02:45.207 --> 00:02:47.126
Tonight. I'ma do what I shoulda done.

67
00:02:47.293 --> 00:02:49.670
I would never hurt you
like that. I love you.

68
00:02:49.837 --> 00:02:52.006
Only person you ever loved is you.

69
00:04:27.434 --> 00:04:29.144
That's why you killed 'em all.

70
00:04:29.311 --> 00:04:31.772
D. Fame. Krystal...

71
00:04:31.897 --> 00:04:33.691
even my own fuckin' father!

72
00:04:36.318 --> 00:04:38.570
That's why I gotta do this right now.

73
00:04:41.573 --> 00:04:44.368
So you can't take nobody else
away from me.

74
00:05:38.547 --> 00:05:39.840
What'd you do?

75
00:05:40.340 --> 00:05:42.134
What the fuck you just do?!

76
00:05:43.469 --> 00:05:45.637
Lou.

77
00:05:48.057 --> 00:05:51.226
Please.

78
00:05:57.066 --> 00:05:58.192
Fuck. no!

79
00:05:59.068 --> 00:06:00.235
Lou!

80
00:06:00.652 --> 00:06:01.987
I'll call a ambulance.

81
00:06:02.654 --> 00:06:04.114
Fuck you gonna tell 'em. Ruben?

82
00:06:09.536 --> 00:06:10.913
Breathe. baby.

83
00:06:20.714 --> 00:06:22.591
I love you. Lou.

84
00:06:27.763 --> 00:06:29.056
I love you.

85
00:06:55.249 --> 00:06:56.249
Go. Kanan.

86
00:06:58.919 --> 00:07:00.337
Now!

87
00:07:26.905 --> 00:07:28.282
Gonna clean this up.

88
00:08:01.106 --> 00:08:02.191
We gotta go.

89
00:08:44.024 --> 00:08:45.442
I wasn't gonna shoot Kanan.

90
00:08:47.819 --> 00:08:49.488
I was just tryin' to get his attention.

91
00:08:51.531 --> 00:08:52.741
What's done is done.

92
00:08:55.202 --> 00:08:56.870
Shit don't even matter no more.

93
00:08:59.539 --> 00:09:00.934
All that matter is that
you can't tell nobody

94
00:09:00.958 --> 00:09:02.292
about what happened here tonight.

95
00:09:04.378 --> 00:09:05.462
Not ever.

96
00:09:07.547 --> 00:09:09.591
And I'm not just talkin' about police.

97
00:09:09.883 --> 00:09:11.385
That shit go without sayin'.

98
00:09:13.887 --> 00:09:16.007
Talkin' about your nearest
and fuckin' dearest. nigga.

99
00:09:17.516 --> 00:09:18.600
Can't tell nobody.

100
00:09:20.143 --> 00:09:21.895
That shit gotta go to the grave with you.

101
00:09:24.189 --> 00:09:25.565
I'm sorry about it.

102
00:09:40.414 --> 00:09:41.748
Yo. Ruben.

103
00:09:43.250 --> 00:09:45.090
Let me hit you off
for this extra work tonight.

104
00:09:46.378 --> 00:09:47.587
I'm good.

105
00:09:48.255 --> 00:09:49.256
Nah.

106
00:09:49.923 --> 00:09:51.550
Nah. this shit was above and beyond.

107
00:10:31.256 --> 00:10:33.050
I ain't got regrets in my life.

108
00:10:33.967 --> 00:10:35.844
I just got shit that's uncomfortable...

109
00:10:36.803 --> 00:10:38.263
that don't ever go away.

110
00:11:59.719 --> 00:12:01.304
I was calling you last night.

111
00:12:02.889 --> 00:12:04.891
There was some wild shit
happening with Kanan.

112
00:12:05.058 --> 00:12:06.226
but you weren't picking up.

113
00:12:06.810 --> 00:12:08.228
I'm busy on some bullshit.

114
00:12:08.979 --> 00:12:10.299
What's the word with your cousin?

115
00:12:11.815 --> 00:12:13.358
He was on one about Aunt Raq.

116
00:12:14.151 --> 00:12:15.777
Was going over there real angry.

117
00:12:16.862 --> 00:12:18.572
I got worried.

118
00:12:18.738 --> 00:12:20.198
Reached Uncle Lou.

119
00:12:20.365 --> 00:12:22.365
He said he was gonna run through
and check on shit.

120
00:12:23.660 --> 00:12:25.537
I ain't heard nothin' about any of that.

121
00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:28.957
Been callin' Kanan and Uncle Lou. but...

122
00:12:29.624 --> 00:12:30.959
neither one of 'em pickin' up.

123
00:12:35.422 --> 00:12:36.422
That's you.

124
00:12:47.225 --> 00:12:48.225
Police.

125
00:12:51.313 --> 00:12:53.023
Marvin Thomas?

126
00:12:55.734 --> 00:12:57.110
Is Louis Thomas your brother?

127
00:13:23.011 --> 00:13:24.262
What you want?

128
00:13:26.223 --> 00:13:27.390
Friends of Rilla's.

129
00:13:28.350 --> 00:13:30.060
From the. studio.

130
00:13:33.813 --> 00:13:35.649
Rilla know Lou Thomas. right?

131
00:13:35.774 --> 00:13:37.442
Yeah. Shh.

132
00:13:37.609 --> 00:13:39.945
Well. we just tryin' to track
him down on some business.

133
00:13:40.111 --> 00:13:42.322
I've been lookin' for Bryan too. It's okay.

134
00:13:42.489 --> 00:13:44.491
He was supposed to come through
and watch the baby.

135
00:13:44.616 --> 00:13:46.677
We met up yesterday so I could
get some stuff from him.

136
00:13:46.701 --> 00:13:47.762
but I ain't heard from him since.

137
00:13:47.786 --> 00:13:49.120
Where'd y'all link?

138
00:13:49.246 --> 00:13:51.540
Outside some raggedy-looking
mall on Merrick.

139
00:13:55.460 --> 00:13:58.171
A'ight. Well. if you see Rilla
before we find him.

140
00:13:58.755 --> 00:14:00.674
tell him Unique came callin'.

141
00:14:01.258 --> 00:14:02.258
All right?

142
00:14:02.300 --> 00:14:03.510
How y'all know Bryan again?

143
00:14:07.222 --> 00:14:08.222
We don't.

144
00:14:08.682 --> 00:14:10.392
But now we know you.

145
00:14:11.393 --> 00:14:13.812
And we know where you
and your baby live.

146
00:14:15.855 --> 00:14:17.232
I-I gotta go.

147
00:14:21.236 --> 00:14:22.988
That mall's Raq's spot.

148
00:14:24.364 --> 00:14:25.574
Tool the fuck up.

149
00:14:37.419 --> 00:14:38.461
Is that your brother?

150
00:14:45.385 --> 00:14:46.511
Is that him?

151
00:14:51.433 --> 00:14:52.809
Yeah. that's Lou.

152
00:15:22.839 --> 00:15:23.839
Was it him?

153
00:15:30.805 --> 00:15:31.848
My God.

154
00:15:38.605 --> 00:15:39.605
My God.

155
00:15:57.624 --> 00:15:59.501
Hey. Good luck. captain.

156
00:16:00.669 --> 00:16:01.753
See ya. captain.

157
00:16:06.716 --> 00:16:07.801
About to head out.

158
00:16:07.967 --> 00:16:09.886
You're gonna be missed.

159
00:16:10.053 --> 00:16:11.179
By everyone.

160
00:16:12.639 --> 00:16:13.973
You do this job long enough.

161
00:16:14.724 --> 00:16:17.268
you gonna make a hell of a lot
more enemies than friends.

162
00:16:18.269 --> 00:16:20.539
Just because they got me riding
out into the fucking sunset

163
00:16:20.563 --> 00:16:22.732
doesn't mean that your work
is done. Garcia.

164
00:16:22.899 --> 00:16:24.459
You wanna get
on the commissioner track.

165
00:16:25.110 --> 00:16:27.445
find who put down Malcolm Howard.

166
00:16:27.570 --> 00:16:29.531
I'm still pressing on the Thomas girl.

167
00:16:29.698 --> 00:16:31.157
Yeah. Burke's old CI.

168
00:16:31.324 --> 00:16:33.076
You need to dig deeper. Garcia.

169
00:16:37.038 --> 00:16:39.540
I'd like to believe I did
more good than harm here.

170
00:16:41.418 --> 00:16:42.877
But that's gonna be God's call.

171
00:16:43.795 --> 00:16:45.505
Getting justice for Howard

172
00:16:46.339 --> 00:16:47.841
would sure help my cause

173
00:16:48.007 --> 00:16:49.926
at them pearly fuckin' gates.
though. Garcia.

174
00:16:55.515 --> 00:16:56.558
Don't let me down.

175
00:17:12.991 --> 00:17:14.617
Where the fuck is this nigga Lou?

176
00:17:16.368 --> 00:17:18.496
I ain't sign up for this babysittin' bullshit.

177
00:17:22.666 --> 00:17:23.917
Nigga. fuck this.

178
00:17:29.424 --> 00:17:30.550
I'm telling you...

179
00:17:32.051 --> 00:17:34.387
if you don't shut the fuck up.

180
00:17:34.554 --> 00:17:35.930
I will kill you and that boy.

181
00:17:36.097 --> 00:17:37.432
- No!
- Bitch.

182
00:17:40.894 --> 00:17:41.894
Finally.

183
00:17:43.980 --> 00:17:45.190
Yo. Lou. that you?

184
00:17:50.945 --> 00:17:51.945
Yo. Lou.

185
00:17:57.118 --> 00:17:58.578
You all right. baby?

186
00:17:58.745 --> 00:17:59.913
They hurt you?

187
00:18:00.079 --> 00:18:02.749
No. no. Just scared. that's all. Shit.

188
00:18:02.916 --> 00:18:04.143
Well. you ain't gotta be scared no more

189
00:18:04.167 --> 00:18:05.247
'cause I'm here. all right?

190
00:18:05.668 --> 00:18:06.795
I got you.

191
00:18:06.920 --> 00:18:08.254
I always got y'all.

192
00:18:25.814 --> 00:18:26.814
Juke know?

193
00:18:29.108 --> 00:18:30.860
She over at Kanan's. telling him.

194
00:18:33.613 --> 00:18:34.882
You gon' want to reach out to him.

195
00:18:34.906 --> 00:18:36.074
He gon' be all fucked up.

196
00:18:37.992 --> 00:18:39.619
Police got thoughts on what happened?

197
00:18:41.579 --> 00:18:43.540
Had to be this motherfucker 'Nique.

198
00:18:44.791 --> 00:18:46.042
He dumped Lou.

199
00:18:47.418 --> 00:18:48.878
Like he was a-a piece of trash.

200
00:18:49.754 --> 00:18:51.214
Like he wasn't even a person.

201
00:18:55.343 --> 00:18:56.743
'Nique must be out his fuckin' mind

202
00:18:56.803 --> 00:18:58.555
comin' after us and Stefano like this.

203
00:19:00.431 --> 00:19:01.474
Juke spoke to Lou.

204
00:19:02.767 --> 00:19:03.847
He was on his way over here

205
00:19:03.935 --> 00:19:05.015
to get in between some shit

206
00:19:05.061 --> 00:19:06.061
you and Kanan was havin'.

207
00:19:06.980 --> 00:19:08.231
He never got here.

208
00:19:09.858 --> 00:19:11.192
And the thing with me and Kanan

209
00:19:11.359 --> 00:19:13.194
wasn't nothin' but the usual drama.

210
00:19:13.361 --> 00:19:15.655
Maybe Ruben saw something
when he was out front.

211
00:19:16.990 --> 00:19:18.575
I ain't talked to him since last night.

212
00:19:19.826 --> 00:19:20.826
I'll reach out.

213
00:19:25.123 --> 00:19:27.125
You handlin' this
a whole lot better than me.

214
00:19:28.501 --> 00:19:29.687
'Cause I'm ready to kill any nigga

215
00:19:29.711 --> 00:19:31.296
who even breathe in my direction.

216
00:19:31.421 --> 00:19:32.421
Shit.

217
00:19:33.631 --> 00:19:35.008
I'm not handlin' anything.

218
00:19:36.009 --> 00:19:37.594
Fuck you want me to do. Marvin?

219
00:19:38.344 --> 00:19:40.471
You just told me that
our baby brother is gone.

220
00:19:40.638 --> 00:19:41.638
I'm fucked up.

221
00:19:42.223 --> 00:19:44.350
I just lost a piece of my fuckin' heart.

222
00:19:45.059 --> 00:19:47.645
I'm just sayin'. you ain't...
you ain't cryin' or nothin'.

223
00:19:47.812 --> 00:19:49.522
We all deal with this shit different.

224
00:19:50.899 --> 00:19:52.775
Don't tell me how to hurt.

225
00:20:01.284 --> 00:20:02.368
Where 'Nique people at?

226
00:20:02.952 --> 00:20:04.555
Pernessa and that boy
is the only leverage

227
00:20:04.579 --> 00:20:05.872
that we got right now.

228
00:20:05.997 --> 00:20:07.165
Where they at?

229
00:20:07.332 --> 00:20:08.875
You can't. Marvin.

230
00:20:09.042 --> 00:20:10.042
I know you want to.

231
00:20:10.126 --> 00:20:11.419
I do too. but you can't.

232
00:20:11.544 --> 00:20:13.171
Tell me where the fuck they are. Raq.

233
00:20:21.888 --> 00:20:22.888
They at the mall.

234
00:20:25.683 --> 00:20:26.893
But you do this...

235
00:20:29.103 --> 00:20:30.313
there ain't no turnin' back.

236
00:20:32.899 --> 00:20:33.899
Lou gone.

237
00:20:35.610 --> 00:20:37.904
Already ain't no turnin' back.

238
00:20:49.248 --> 00:20:50.416
I called him.

239
00:20:56.422 --> 00:20:58.091
Told him about you goin' to Raq's.

240
00:21:02.095 --> 00:21:03.805
He said he was gonna go over there.

241
00:21:06.683 --> 00:21:08.101
I never saw him.

242
00:21:19.404 --> 00:21:21.739
All the fucked up shit this family into...

243
00:21:25.660 --> 00:21:27.328
and I still can't believe he's gone.

244
00:21:29.497 --> 00:21:32.041
You think I'd expect it.

245
00:21:32.208 --> 00:21:33.793
or be ready for it.

246
00:21:34.293 --> 00:21:35.461
or some shit.

247
00:21:36.045 --> 00:21:38.047
but I guess I just thought...

248
00:21:38.798 --> 00:21:40.466
for all our bullshit

249
00:21:40.633 --> 00:21:41.926
that we was untouchable.

250
00:21:46.097 --> 00:21:48.016
Nobody's untouchable.

251
00:21:55.523 --> 00:21:56.649
Word.

252
00:22:10.329 --> 00:22:11.914
How you settin' up. Breeze?

253
00:22:12.040 --> 00:22:14.167
Southside ain't no different
from East New York.

254
00:22:15.001 --> 00:22:16.919
Blocks change. work stay the same.

255
00:22:17.795 --> 00:22:19.630
You just make sure you get yourself

256
00:22:19.797 --> 00:22:21.549
a few safe spots out there.

257
00:22:22.341 --> 00:22:24.927
Somewhere where you can post up
when shit gets perilous

258
00:22:25.094 --> 00:22:27.138
'cause shit will get perilous. nephew.

259
00:22:27.889 --> 00:22:29.640
I ain't heard from Kanan or Unique.

260
00:22:30.099 --> 00:22:31.392
They'll come around.

261
00:22:31.976 --> 00:22:33.576
Shit. they ain't got nowhere else to go.

262
00:22:34.145 --> 00:22:35.730
Still don't understand why I gotta fuck

263
00:22:35.897 --> 00:22:36.939
with this nigga Unique.

264
00:22:37.690 --> 00:22:39.484
Kanan's a special case.

265
00:22:39.650 --> 00:22:40.693
We know this.

266
00:22:41.360 --> 00:22:44.072
But this other motherfucker
redundant as hell.

267
00:22:44.197 --> 00:22:45.907
Why we need him when we got me?

268
00:22:46.032 --> 00:22:48.451
He still got soldiers out on those streets.

269
00:22:48.576 --> 00:22:50.620
